### 0 — bus up
sextant bus up
 url: <URL>
 discovery: <PATH>/bus.json
 operator: <PATH>/operator.creds

issue a client identity (the bus mints it; keys stay in the bus):
 sextant clients register <name> --store <PATH>

Ctrl-C to drain and stop.

### 1 — issuance (operator mints alice; bob self-enrolls)
registered alice as <ULID:alice>
 creds: <PATH>/alice.creds
enrolled as <ULID:bob>
 creds: <PATH>/bob.creds

### 2 — message with an unforgeable author
published to msg.topic.plan
[msg.topic.plan] <ULID> <<ULID:alice>> {"hello":"world"}

### 3 — shared artifact via compare-and-set
the-plan now at revision 1
the-plan now at revision 2
sextant: sextant: artifact.update: bus: artifact "the-plan" changed since revision 1
the-plan (revision 2)
{"title":"v2"}

### 4 — the live directory shows presence
<ULID:alice> alice worker epoch=1 online
<ULID:bob> bob reviewer epoch=1 online
(2 clients)

### 5 — durable identity across reconnect (offline, then back online)
<ULID:alice> alice worker epoch=1 online
<ULID:bob> bob reviewer epoch=1 offline
(2 clients)
<ULID:alice> alice worker epoch=1 online
<ULID:bob> bob reviewer epoch=1 online
(2 clients)

### 6 — retire decommissions the identity
retired <ULID:bob>
<ULID:alice> alice worker epoch=1 online
(1 clients)

